---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---
<PageLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Fugerit Coding Org — an Italian open source organization creating Java libraries and tools since 2014."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="badge">About</span>
      <h1>Fugerit Coding Org</h1>
      <p>An open source Java development organization from Italy.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container about-layout">

      <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="about-block">
          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          <p>
            The main purpose of <strong>Fugerit Coding Org</strong> is to create simple, well-tested libraries
            and tools that make Java development easier, faster, and more reliable.
          </p>
          <p>
            We believe great software is built on great foundations. Instead of reinventing the wheel,
            we stand on the shoulders of proven open source projects (Apache FOP, Apache POI, Freemarker,
            and many others) and build a coherent layer that simplifies their use.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-block">
          <h2>What We Build</h2>
          <p>There are three main categories of projects hosted by Fugerit Coding Org:</p>
          <ol class="about-list">
            <li>
              <strong>Core libraries</strong> — foundational multi-module Maven projects:
              fj-bom, fj-lib (Jupiter), fj-doc (Venus), fj-daogen (Mars), fj-universe.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Tools</strong> — purpose-built command-line tools and Maven plugins for
              specific tasks: OpenAPI documentation, SQL export, GraalVM native image support,
              GitHub issue export.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Documentation &amp; Quickstarts</strong> — ready-to-run examples and guides
              to help you get started quickly.
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="about-block">
          <h2>Quality Commitment</h2>
          <p>
            All projects are continuously monitored by <a href="https://sonarcloud.io/organizations/fugerit-org/projects" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">SonarCloud</a>
            for code quality and security issues. Every library is released under the permissive
            <strong>Apache License 2.0</strong> and published to Maven Central.
          </p>
          <p>
            Most projects target <strong>Java 8+</strong> for maximum compatibility, while newer
            modules take advantage of modern Java features where appropriate.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-block">
          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Questions, suggestions, or collaboration proposals are always welcome.
            Reach out via email or open an issue on GitHub.
          </p>
          <div class="about-ctas">
            <a href="mailto:d@fugerit.org" class="btn btn-primary" id="contact-email-btn">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
              d@fugerit.org
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/fugerit-org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline" id="about-github-btn">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0 0 24 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/></svg>
              GitHub Org
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SIDEBAR -->
      <aside class="about-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h4>Organization</h4>
          <dl class="about-dl">
            <dt>Name</dt>
            <dd>Fugerit Coding Org</dd>
            <dt>Location</dt>
            <dd>Italy 🇮🇹</dd>
            <dt>License</dt>
            <dd>Apache-2.0</dd>
            <dt>Repositories</dt>
            <dd>113+</dd>
            <dt>Primary Language</dt>
            <dd>Java</dd>
          </dl>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h4>Resources</h4>
          <ul class="sidebar-links">
            <li><a href="https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/fugerit/java/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" id="release-repo-link">Release Repository ↗</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://oss.sonatype.org/content/repositories/snapshots/org/fugerit/java/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" id="snapshot-repo-link">Snapshot Repository ↗</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://sonarcloud.io/organizations/fugerit-org/projects" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" id="sonar-org-link">SonarCloud Quality ↗</a></li>
            <li><a href="http://github-org.fugerit.org/profile/credits.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" id="credits-link">Credits ↗</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card sidebar-thanks">
          <h4>Special Thanks</h4>
          <p>Proud recipients of open source support from:</p>
          <ul class="sidebar-links">
            <li>
              <a href="https://www.jetbrains.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" id="jetbrains-about-link">
                JetBrains — OSS Community License ↗
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://sonarcloud.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" id="sonarcloud-about-link">
                SonarCloud ↗
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://www.codacy.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" id="codacy-about-link">
                Codacy ↗
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://snyk.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" id="snyk-about-link">
                Snyk ↗
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>

    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 9rem 0 4rem;
    background: var(--gradient-hero);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--clr-border);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .page-hero .badge { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .page-hero h1 { color: var(--clr-white); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .page-hero p { font-size: 1.05rem; max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .about-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-content { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 3rem; }

  .about-block h2 { color: var(--clr-white); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.4rem; }
  .about-block p  { font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .about-block p a { color: var(--clr-accent); }
  .about-block p a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  .about-list {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .about-list li { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--clr-text-dim); }
  .about-list li strong { color: var(--clr-text); }

  .about-ctas { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.75rem; margin-top: 1rem; }

  /* Sidebar */
  .about-sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 90px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .sidebar-card {
    background: var(--clr-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--clr-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .sidebar-card h4 {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--clr-text-dim);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-dl {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 0.5rem 1rem;
  }

  dt { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--clr-text-dim); }
  dd { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--clr-text); font-weight: 500; }

  .sidebar-links {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .sidebar-links a {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--clr-text-dim);
    transition: color var(--transition);
  }

  .sidebar-links a:hover { color: var(--clr-accent); }

  .sidebar-thanks p { font-size: 0.82rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-sidebar { position: static; }
  }
</style>
